name: Watching Over America
description:
This image, "Watching Over America" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to depict the American Eagle representing and watching over America and its Core Values. The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer.
